casebody.data:
No. 120,

Orig.

New Jersey v. New York. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 516 U. S. 1026.]

Motion of the Special Master for award of fees and expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $144,837.50 for the period November 18, 1995, through May 15, 1996, to be paid equally by the parties.
